DUODICIMO CHAPTER II.

20
00:01:31,882 --> 00:01:33,524
OLGERINE PORPUS DOT.

21
00:01:34,145 --> 00:01:34,646
A pirate.

22
00:01:35,166 --> 00:01:35,807
Very savage.

23
00:01:35,907 --> 00:01:38,271
He is only found, I think, in the Pacific.

24
00:01:38,932 --> 00:01:43,158
He is somewhat larger than the Husiporpus, but much of the same general make.

25
00:01:43,999 --> 00:01:46,143
Provoke him, and he will buckle to a shark.

26
00:01:47,184 --> 00:01:51,190
I have lowered for him many times, but never yet saw him captured.

27
00:01:52,672 --> 00:01:53,293
Book 3.

28
